trans-unit.source: Represents the <xref uid="langword_csharp_<federationConfiguration>" name="<federationConfiguration>" href=""></xref> element in a configuration file.
trans-unit.target: 表示<xref uid="langword_csharp_<federationConfiguration>" name="<federationConfiguration>" href=""></xref>配置文件中的元素。

trans-unit.source: This class cannot be inherited.
trans-unit.target: 此类不能被继承。

trans-unit.source: The `<federationConfiguration>` element contains the settings that configure the WS-Federation Authentication Module (<xref:System.IdentityModel.Services.WSFederationAuthenticationModule>) and the Session Authentication Module (<xref:System.IdentityModel.Services.SessionAuthenticationModule>).
trans-unit.target: `<federationConfiguration>`元素包含配置 WS 联合身份验证模块的设置 (<xref:System.IdentityModel.Services.WSFederationAuthenticationModule>) 和会话身份验证模块 (<xref:System.IdentityModel.Services.SessionAuthenticationModule>)。</xref:System.IdentityModel.Services.SessionAuthenticationModule> </xref:System.IdentityModel.Services.WSFederationAuthenticationModule>

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of the <xref href="System.IdentityModel.Services.Configuration.FederationConfigurationElement"></xref> class.
trans-unit.target: 初始化的新实例<xref href="System.IdentityModel.Services.Configuration.FederationConfigurationElement"></xref>类。

trans-unit.target: 获取或设置子<xref uid="langword_csharp_<cookieHandler>" name="<cookieHandler>" href=""></xref>元素。

trans-unit.source: The `<cookieHandler>` element configures the <xref:System.IdentityModel.Services.CookieHandler> object that the Session Authentication Module (<xref:System.IdentityModel.Services.SessionAuthenticationModule>) uses to read and write cookies.
trans-unit.target: `<cookieHandler>`元素会配置<xref:System.IdentityModel.Services.CookieHandler>对象会话身份验证模块 (<xref:System.IdentityModel.Services.SessionAuthenticationModule>) 用于读取和写入 cookie。</xref:System.IdentityModel.Services.SessionAuthenticationModule> </xref:System.IdentityModel.Services.CookieHandler>

trans-unit.target: `name`属性设置要与此关联的名称`<federationConfiguration>`元素。

trans-unit.target: 如果名称属性为`null`，当前元素是默认联合身份验证配置。
